On the road, the beaver feather ball full of justice, the timid but bragging hare big teeth, the congenital dysplasia yellow antelope dwarf egg, wild horse and wild crane friends, etc. helped each other to overcome various difficulties and obstacles, tempered their minds, and gained With friendship and joy, it gradually grew into a legend of the grassland. The content of the film is inspirational and quiet, entertaining and entertaining.(translated from douban)

synopsis: The story takes place in the 21st century candy market. An old Wu head (grandfather) who is often confused as a "god of sleep"; Wu Dalong (dad) who is a safety supervisor who often causes safety accidents; Qiao Sixi (mom) who has exploded hair and is known for his patience; Candy Sea Elementary School The student, the erring king Wu Jiale (son); the talented boy plus the melancholy Wu Jiamei (daughter); and finally, there is a pair of pacifiers, always imitating others and with a natural cynical rock cell. Year-old BABY Wu Jiaxin. These six people formed an ordinary family in the candy sea market-the Wu family. In this family, the mother's inadequacy in financial management often caused economic difficulties; the "fighting" between Wu Jiale and Wu Jiamei's brothers and sisters, Wu Jiaxin's naughty It constitutes a ridiculous event in the story, but the ending can always bring you deep touch and endless joy. title: Mo Bi Jingling
synopsis: "Magic Coin Wizard" takes eight young children with their own growth characteristics as the protagonists of the story. They are respectively given the mission of saving mankind. Each is equipped with the god of justice in the elves world-the god of elven energy coins to summon " "Magic coin beasts", support each other, grow up and fight against the evil demon of the world of elves—Lucifer sent the evil forces to destroy the real world to fight strongly. In the end, the eight warriors worked together to defeat the devil’s minions and saved the real world through various hardships. , And rescue the god king, help the god king defeat the demon king Lucifer and save the magic coin world. In the process, the children learned to be brave, strong, honest and trustworthy, united, and gained friendship. "Magic Coin Wizard" is a magical masterpiece that is jointly produced by Shanghai Ruise Culture Communication Co., Ltd., Zhejiang Yongkang Langxiu Culture Media Company and Guangdong Sanbao. title: Niguang Zhi Chan
synopsis: The story is set in an energy-poor world. The protagonist of the story, Bain, grew up alone, with a lonely and indifferent personality. When Bain was twelve years old, he was banished from the transoceanic train to the territory ruled by the new energy company ‘Hilter’. On the train, he ran into the female protagonist Sharo, who was weak in nature but had blood-like unclean hair. Baine was killed in a new territory due to his extreme personality, and the second male protagonist rescued Baine in a life-threatening crisis. The two are getting closer and closer, and gradually discover the conspiracy of the new energy company "Hilter". Zhiye's innocence slowly melted Bain's indifference, and the ever-growing friendship and love led him to become a "hermit". The whole story revolves around the gradual growth of Bain in the new energy world, encountering a group of comrades with similar destiny but different personalities, as well as various struggles and conspiracies that continue to arise in this new energy world.(translated from baidu baike)

title: Xiao Rui Yu Da Mowang
synopsis: "Xiao Rui and the Big Devil" revolves around the story of fighting between five little treasures headed by Xiao Rui and the weird inventor, the big devil. It is humorous, entertaining and entertaining, and integrates scientific, intellectual, educational and Entertaining as a whole, let the small audience be inspired: unite and cooperate with partners, can better overcome difficulties. 　　 A long, long time ago, there was a quiet small village-Rococo in the quiet folk song forest. The unicorn beast Xiaorui lives here, accompanied by his heirloom-the magic disk, and four lively and brave friends. In the distant place Sharer TV, there is a single-minded production genius-the big devil, who wants to rule the world and get the world's most fun toys. With his genius mind, he built a movable "toy castle" and packed all his whimsical ideas in it. However, on this day, the Great Devil encountered a problem... (translated from douban)

title: Xiao Rui Yu Da Mowang Zhi Kuaile Leitai
synopsis: The Great Demon, who was frowning because he couldn't pay the electricity bill, accidentally discovered the letter left by his ancestors. He learned that Rococo Village originally belonged to the Great Demon family, so he immediately rushed to Rococo to ask for the village. Xiao Rui and the others had a dispute with the Great Demon King at the entrance of the village, waking up Grandpa Land in the Folk Song Forest. Grandpa Land decided to use the game to determine the outcome and determine the ownership of Rococo Village. Thus, the happy arena between Xiao Rui and the big devil began. In the end, Xiao Rui won the victory, and the castle was confiscated because the big devil did not pay the electricity bill in time! But the kind grandma redeemed the castle and leased it to the big devil so that he can continue to use it. However, the big devil always hoped that he could really return to his castle, and it happened that a little shopkeeper came to the village and left a talking magic box. The Magic Box declares to everyone that it can help people realize a wish. Because the little friends and the big demon have their desires to realize, so both sides are vying for this magic box. Finally, the magic box decides to use a new type of competition to determine the right to belong to the desire, and a new round of competition begins again. . In the end, the little friends won, but the last wish was wasted due to a mismatch. Although she couldn't help grandma realize her wish, she was still very happy, so the friends were relieved and everyone was happy. The happy grandma felt that the courage of the great devil was commendable, so she took the initiative to return the toy castle to the great devil. Both parties are happy. (translated from douban)

In order to stop this conspiracy, the Shenrui family relied on the power of the light star to launch a thrilling battle of the century, and finally defeated the fleshfoot family, controlled the dark matter scepter, and stored it in a secret place. Two hundred years later, the queen of fleshy feet, the Demon King, made a comeback and released the dark matter scepter in an attempt to realize his family's wishes! The Dark Matter Scepter is about to return, and the whole world is at stake! Xiao Rui, the descendant of the Shenrui family, and his friends decided to go to the Five Kingdoms of Jinmu, Water, Fire, Earth, and activate the power to control the Dark Matter Scepter—Light, to re-control the Dark Matter Scepter. However, the road ahead is long, and too many unknown dangers are waiting for them. Can Xiao Rui defeat the Demon King and bring peace to the world? (translated from iqiyi)

It has three helpers-Crow Wu Xiaoya, Big Boar Zhu Jiujie, and Little Field Mouse Xiaobei, determined to take "Happy Farm" as its own. As a result, a tense and interesting struggle started on the "Happy Farm"...(translated from douban)

From then on, these five boys were closely connected with the fate of the city and the survival of the treasure. Secondly, Jin Ling is the princess of Hades. The brave "five elements boy" experienced all kinds of difficulties, and also made the people of Tiancheng wake up. The cowardly and selfish citizens of Ruyi Rabbit stepped forward, relying on unity and finally defeated the people of Hades fort, and saved Tiancheng's own beautiful home. In the protagonist's hard and tortuous defense battle, the audience received a major safety education in environmental safety and urban safety, and at the same time revealed the profound theme of protecting the green environment.(translated rom douban)

title: Jie Mi Xiong Zhi Mohuan Maxi Tuan
synopsis: The story of "Magic Circus of Jamie Bear" tells that Sweetheart Valley established the "Magic Circus", and Jamie Bear, who is good at magic performances, became the lead actor and director. Friends such as Mimi Xiong and Xiaoxiong also joined the performance team. Everyone worked together to make the circus show more and more popular. Once, Jamie Bear and Mimi Bear came to the Moonlight City Playground to play. After having fun, the friends suddenly sprouted the grand goal of building a Sweetheart Valley in Sweetheart Valley, a playground for the children themselves. So, the friends started a wonderful circus tour, and finally, after hard work, finally raised the first funds for the construction of the "Sweetheart Mountain Valley Playground". On the other hand, the smiling lion was unwilling to live a hard life in the harsh environment of the foggy forest, and invited the wise man among the lions, the sheep lion, to plan the revival of the overlord lion group. The Sheep Lion resorted to tricks and tricks to deceive the residents of Sweetheart Valley, so that the Overlord Lion could occupy the beautiful Sweetheart Valley by himself, but the insidious tricks were exposed one by one by the residents of Sweetheart Valley. As a result, the sheep lion resorted to a more vicious double conspiracy: 1. Using the super allergenic factor of ghost perfume to cause allergies to the residents of the mountain valley, causing civil unrest in the sweetheart valley. 2. Find and operate the weather control device to make the weather in the Sweetheart Valley so bad that it cannot be inhabited, so that the residents of the valley can relocate automatically, and then achieve the ugly purpose of letting the lion occupy the Sweetheart Valley. Jamie Bear and the residents of the Sweetheart Valley fight against the bad weather together, and finally learn the truth about the deterioration of the climate. The brave Jamie Bear breaks into the foggy forest and fights wits with the lions with the help of the residents of Sweetheart Valley. Yong finally cleverly expelled the Overlord Lion and restored the peace and harmony of Sweetheart Valley. (translated from douban)

title: Jie Mi Xiong Zhi Tianxin Jijie Hao
synopsis: The Jamie Bear family lives in the sweetheart valley with charming scenery, fresh air and beautiful environment. Jamie Bear’s greatest hobby is to constantly create wonderful magic tricks to entertain people around him and be proud of it. Jamie Xiong has many good friends, such as the cute Mimi, the weird little bear, the sweet tooth, the spectacled bear who loves poetry, the self-righteous pop bear... Jamie and his friends are here Sweetheart Valley lives a happy life. 　　 However, all this originally good was broken by a group of hateful lions. 　　 It turned out that the Overlord Lions, who originally lived in the misty forest, have always coveted the beautiful environment of the Sweetheart Valley, and they wanted to occupy the Sweetheart Valley, so they repeatedly launched an attack on the Sweetheart Valley. The faith in justice and homeland defense supports Jamie Xiong and his friends. They have used wisdom and courage to defeat the lion king, destroy the evil power of the lion king, and restore the temporary peace and harmony of the Sweetheart Valley. 　　 When the defeated lion clan was forced to exile, they were supported by mysterious people. With the airship as its base camp, the Overlord Lion regained its strength and started a new round of evil plans—initiating a new round of plans to capture the Sweetheart Valley, delusional to regain its goal of occupying the Sweetheart Valley. 　　 Under the guidance and assistance of mysterious people, the Overlord Lions have continuously developed various weapons with powerful lethality, and have repeatedly launched attacks on the Sweetheart Valley. Jamie Xiong and his friends who love their hometown, in order to protect their homeland, work together to start a battle of wits and courage with the lion king. In this arduous struggle, Jamie Xiong practiced the magic secrets taught by Master Kakaxiong. Little Bear worked assiduously on high-tech according to the weapon secrets. Members of the Justice League, such as Ogi Xiong, offered suggestions. The faith in upholding justice and defending their homes supported the residents of Sweetheart Valley. Jamie Xiong, who defeated the King Lion again and again with wisdom and courage, finally called on the residents of Sweetheart Valley to defend the valley at a critical juncture. Called by the Horn of Justice, the residents of Sweetheart Valley and all the members of the Justice League in the world worked together to destroy the evil power of the Overlord Lion and restore the tranquility and peace of Sweetheart Valley. (translated from douban)

title: Jie Mi Xiong Zhi Mo Ping Da Maoxian
synopsis: While Sweetheart's Vase was activated by the Sweetheart's horn, it also activated the King of the Bottle trapped in the Sweetheart's Vase. He enslaved the inhabitants of the world in the bottle-the cat tribe. In order to leave Aquarius and control the world, the King of the Bottle must accumulate enough sweetheart energy. Therefore, the King of Magic Bottle will not hesitate to inhale the residents of the entire Sweetheart Valley into the bottle to extract their sweetheart energy-life energy. In order to save the residents of Sweetheart Valley, under the leadership of the horn fairy who is the incarnation of Sweetheart Horn, Jamie Bear, Little Bear, Mimi Bear, Spectacled Bear, and Black Bear Bobo came to the world of Aquarius. With the help of the five holy armor powers, Constantly self-training, self-improvement, passing the test, reaching the seventh level of Aquarius World, using the faith of sweetheart energy love to defeat the king of the magic bottle, and rescued the residents of Aquarius World and Sweetheart Valley. However, after winning the last piece of porcelain core, Zihe became a mysterious map, which turned out to be the biggest secret of Sweetheart Valley. Next, a new challenge will begin again...(translated from baidu baike)

synopsis: The film tells the story of the wheat circle, cocoa and pet "Meatballs" riding on the spacecraft "Messiah", flying down the wind to Taiwan, the island of Taiwan, and encountering a Taiwanese girl Zhizhi who is kind but always good at doing bad things and her pet "Grand Theft Cat" ". Led by Zhizhi, Maiquan and others toured the famous scenic spots in Taiwan, followed the "Rogue" Zhizhi to do a bunch of funny and fun "good things", and experienced the life philosophy of "there is nothing difficult in the world, only the people with the heart". The play aims to use animation to let children understand the long history, culture and beautiful scenery of Taiwan.(translated from douban)

title: Zhi Qu Haidi Cheng
synopsis: During the trip, Maiquan, Cocoa and their pet dog discovered that the East China Sea was polluted and threatened by the underwater city. The three protagonists drive the spacecraft into the underwater city, use their wisdom to solve the secret between the underwater city and Hemudu, and defeat the owner of the underwater city. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Xi Xiao Yijia Qin
synopsis: The wheat circle who just entered junior high school likes to be clever, but his grades are not very satisfactory. Mr. Mak is a workaholic and has been looking forward to promotion. Mrs. Mai is enthusiastic and easy to learn. The gluttonous and sleepy puppy is the "pistachio" of the family. Suddenly, the perfect cousin, Coco, is the enemy of the wheat circle. Five family members with different personalities collided and rubbed each other, triggering hilarious and warm stories one after another, which reflected the growth of young people and the importance of a harmonious family. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Chao Shiqi Xingqiu Lixian Ji
synopsis: Maiquan cocoa and puppy meatballs happened to meet a "dog" named Yuball at Hemudu, and the fishballs and meatballs immediately became good friends. One day, the fish balls suddenly disappeared. While looking for the fish balls, Maiquan Coco and Puppy Meatballs learned that the fish balls were actually cosmic creatures, and the parent star of the fish balls, the Superstone planet, was plotting to invade the earth. In order to retrieve the fish balls and defend the earth, Maiquan Cocoa and Puppy Meatballs flew to the universe on the Dayang Mei spacecraft. Through the joint efforts of everyone, the aggression plan of the Superstone Planet was terminated, and mankind finally avoided a catastrophe. At this time, Yuball had to say goodbye to Maiquan Coco and Puppy Meatball. (translated form baidu baike)

title: Shen Quan Yong Chuang Jixie Cheng
synopsis: The original beautiful world has gradually become desertified due to over-development of cities and villages, and a strange disease that has gradually mechanized humans has also broken out. In order to find life-saving herbs and defeat the evil mechanical king, the god dog brave and his partners embarked on a journey to the mechanical city. With the help of their partners, the dog brave defeated the King of Machines and saved people's gradually desolate hearts. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Dongwu Xingxing Da Tanxian
synopsis: The puppies of Mai Quan's family inherited super powers from their ancestors. One day, he received a call for help from Animal Planet, and the evil forces sealed in the Arctic ice sheet are recovering. Therefore, he led a group of animal companions from the southern hemisphere and began to expel the evil forces' minions. On the way, he met many companions, overcome various difficulties, went deep into the center of the Arctic ice sheet, and finally sealed the evil forces again. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Xiaoyuan Qiyi Shijian Bu

In the class, there is a wheat circle who loves to be clever but is always the third to last in the exam, there are excellent grades, beautiful and cute wheat circle cousin Coco, there are simple and enthusiastic fat people and scientific family born, strong squad leader biscuit, and her Classmates and teachers with very different personalities. One day, the Doudou Stars are coming! Maiquan, cocoa, meatballs and friends have to fight the pranksters in order to maintain a peaceful campus life. Interesting stories are constantly being staged. (translated from baidu baike)

title: Wuzi Shuo
synopsis: The outline of the story of "Wu Zi Shuo" was adapted from Cai Zhizhong's cartoon. The whole article is divided into five parts: "Zhuang Zi", "Lao Zi", "Mencius", "Confucius", "Sun Zi". Using exaggerated and unrealistic brushwork, the five people’s broad and profound philosophical principles, principles of handling, thoughts and concepts and other complex content, using humorous and interesting painting techniques, simple and easy to understand reasoning methods, using storytelling as the carrier, through many interesting Small stories, such as character stories, animal stories, landscapes, flowers and birds, and newly-edited stories, can be expressed flexibly. The whole story contains a lot of easy and interesting fables, which are simple and easy to understand, and have high learning value for modern people. 　　 Introduction to the Characters of "Five Sons" Lao Tzu: is a representative of Taoism, his "Tao De Jing" is full of wisdom, and the harmonious society he advocates, the quiet and inaction thought has influenced the history of more than two thousand years. Zhuangzi: Ancient Chinese philosopher, good at expressing the philosophical meaning of things with allegories, witty and humorous. Confucius: Ancient Chinese thinker, educator, and representative of Chinese Confucianism. He advocated loving others with benevolence. Mencius: Representative of Confucianism: He inherited the ideas of Confucius, traveled around the country and worked hard to realize the ideal of benevolent governance. Sun Tzu: A well-known military strategist and thinker in ancient China, he is the foremost master of military science in Chinese history. He is the author of the book "Sun Tzu's Art of War". (translated form douban)

title: Shikong Shaonian
synopsis: The story takes place in the world 1,000 years from now. In that era, scientists have invented the technology of space-time transition, enabling people to travel through different time and space, connecting with the future and exploring the past; they can travel in every corner of the universe. You can step into other dimensional spaces. As a result, the level of human science and technology has also been greatly improved, but at the same time, it has inevitably brought some troubles. The world has become diversified due to the invention of jump technology. Humans in the past, present, and future; creatures on different planets; life in different dimensional universes are increasingly communicating with each other. Different civilizations and concepts are intertwined, causing many misunderstandings. And contradictions; man-made malicious destruction has caused many dangers. Therefore, Christopher Owen, the developer of the jump technology, gathered the three children of Kuya, Xia Yu, and Chen to form an organization called "Guardians of Time and Space", which is responsible for solving all kinds of troubles caused by the chaos of time and space. Cuya and his friend Xia Yuhechen, in the process of traveling through different time and space, arrested criminals who maliciously disrupted the order of time and space; tracked the aliens who made black holes and tried to engulf the earth; resisted natural disasters; escorted the lost children in different time and space back. Home; protect ancient alien guests; meet the mysterious prophet Nostradamus; visit the weird Meilu restaurant; participate in future shooting competitions... These stories not only happened in different countries and eras, but also in various Such an incredible planet and dimensional space. The protagonists use their wisdom and courage to overcome all kinds of difficulties. The unity and mutual assistance in the adventures made them understand what true friendship is. 　　The story unfolds in the form of a drama, and the audience will follow the protagonist and wander through the wonderful science fiction. The fantasy world and the bizarre events that occurred in the story are based on rigorous scientific theories and a rich imagination, which happens naturally. While watching the film, the audience can also learn a variety of scientific knowledge, so that cartoons are no longer limited to unbounded and unfounded pure fantasy. At the same time, the film also conveys to people "As long as everyone's efforts, our dream today will be tomorrow's reality, and a beautiful future is in front of you and me". This is the unique difference between science fiction and other fantasy. , It has a kind of achievability, motivating people to move forward, inspiring thoughts, guiding our exploration of scientific knowledge, inspiring our imagination of the future world, realizing our hope for a better life, let us look at this from a new perspective world.(translated from douban)

title: Hei! Xingxing Hu
synopsis: Star Fox and The magic mother lives in a magical world full of fantasy colors. On the 5th birthday of Star Fox, the magic mother decided to teach him the magic of lollipops. Each magic is recorded on a magical magic card. This kind of magic is all around our lives. As long as we look for it with our heart, we will be able to find it. Once we find and possess these magical magic cards, we will find that the relationship between people is sweeter than candy. Deep in the remote magic forest, there is a beautiful hut called the magic hut. Under the guidance of the owner of the magic house, the magic mother, Xingxinghu and his friends grew up happily here. Our protagonist is the star fox-a lively, smart, and playful little fox. He is a little man. Although he is a little bit stinky and likes to be praised by others, he is warm and kind, brave and persistent. In the magical forest full of magic, weird things often happen. These strange things make every day in the magical forest a wonderful day. (translated from baidu baike)

Kuza's various behaviors posed a great threat to Paobu Village. At this time, the Guardian of Light will appear. He is brave, clever, firm, strong, and bravely confronts the Dark Messenger. The Guardian of Light succeeded in smashing the dark messenger's plan every time, expelling the darkness, returning the light to everyone, making Xiao Zheng Xing full of joy again, and then leaving silently. title: Jia You Jiang Hu
synopsis: This play tells a series of stories that happened to Paste. The paste of the fourth grader of Huaer Primary School is a smart and lively little boy. He often has some wonderful ideas in his mind, and he will try his best to make his own ideas become reality. He likes to make some inventions and creations. He used to make the TV at home. Modified into a radio...The paste is also very optimistic. When he encounters troubles, he will always face positively and optimistically...The paste is a bit wise and foolish, even if he encounters a robber, he can calmly deal with the robber and sap the robber wisely. . Paste is like a friend in normal life. It also cares about small things. When celebrating birthdays, it will compare whether the gifts everyone gives is good enough. When you are lazy, you will find excuses for not being able to complete your learning tasks. The dialogue filled with innocence makes people dumbfounded. Pasty's father Old Pasty wanted to train Paste into a new generation of superman. Because he compared with Marilian's father, he often had high requirements for Paste, such as let Paste go to training classes or let Paste learn. All kinds of talents, and the paste does not disappoint. These training and talent learning have become interesting stories. Learning the piano can attract the police, and learning quick calculations has turned into learning music... and the paste often grabs everything. Opportunity is self-reliant, hoping to support a sky on its own. Not only did he cook the food by himself, but he also repaired the plumbing at home by himself...there is paste at home and happiness at home. Such a happy little boy living in his own world will always have infinite creativity and infinite Surprise, let's take a look! (translated from baidu baike)

title: Xin Shaonian Huang Feihong
synopsis: In the late Qing Dynasty, Huang Feihong, a native of Foshan, Guangdong, was born in poverty. But his low status did not change his heart of being a chivalrous man. With the help of his childhood friend Thirteenth Aunt, Feihong got the guidance of the martial arts master Su Qier and began a hard career in martial arts. Under the meticulous cultivation of Master, after many years of hard work, Feihong Wugong has made great progress. In the Tai Chi Gate, Xiao Feihong tried his forefront for the first time, breaking through the fist formation, the god tiger, the fire demon, the stone unicorn, the stone soldier formation, the wooden figure, etc., and finally succeeded in breaking through the barriers. Finally, he broke through the Tai Chi gate, formally became a disciple of the Beggar Gang. Feihong, who was determined to benefit the people, opened a "Baozhilin" in Foshan. On the one hand, he opened a restaurant to collect pork Rong and Liang Kuan as apprentices, and on the other hand, he was famous for treating diseases for the people. At the same time, Foshan's wealthy gentry Young Master Qu colluded with foreigners and colluded with the government to sell Fushou Ointment to poison the common people. After hearing the news, Feihong and Lin Zexu, who had come to ban smoking, destroyed the smoking hall, destroyed the opium, and shattered Young Master Qu's dream of getting rich. Young Master Qu was always ashamed and angry, and he laid down a conspiracy to put Feihong to death, but the defenseless Feihong gradually fell into the conspiracy of Young Master Qu.(translated from douban)

title: Kangri Xiao Qibing
synopsis: The story is based on the rocky fate of Huhu and Dandan. A tragic story of blood and fire is filmed in a comedy fashion. The cartoon follows the characteristics of the two brothers. The story tells them that their family was destroyed, dependent on each other, displaced, and dealt with in the bloody wind of the Japanese invasion of China. The wolf’s den, through the wind and danger, from the isolated and helpless passive resistance to the little warriors who consciously resist the Japanese, show the brothers and the Japanese and puppet forces fighting wit and courage. (translated from douban)
